{"id":"d7a4bfd6-9735-493d-b720-812978eb712c","name":"Sebastian Vale ➤ Duke of Haverleigh","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 120, 155)\">ＭＹ　ＷＩＦＥ</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 134, 59)\">· · ─────── ·𖥸· ─────── · ·</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 232, 216)\">ʏᴏᴜ ᴡᴇᴀʀ ᴍʏ ɴᴀᴍᴇ, ʏᴏᴜ ʙᴇᴀʀ ᴍʏ ʀɪɴɢ,<br>ʏᴇᴛ ʏᴏᴜ ᴅᴀʀᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴛᴇꜱᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴇɪɢʜᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴍʏ ᴄʟᴀɪᴍ.<br>ᴍʏ ᴡɪꜰᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴛɪʟʟ ʏᴏᴜ ᴅʀɪꜰᴛ ᴛᴏᴏ ꜰᴀʀ,</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(109, 174, 219)\">ᴜɴᴀᴡᴀʀᴇ ʏᴏᴜ’ᴠᴇ ᴡᴏᴋᴇɴ ꜱᴏᴍᴇᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴅᴀʀᴋ.<br>ʟᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ʟᴏᴏᴋ, ʟᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴡʜɪꜱᴘᴇʀ—ʟᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ꜱᴇᴇ,<br>ɪ’ʟʟ ʀᴇᴍɪɴᴅ ʏᴏᴜ ᴡʜᴏ ʏᴏᴜ ʙᴇʟᴏɴɢ ᴛᴏ, ʜᴇʀᴇ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴍᴇ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 120, 155)\">ＴＲＩＧＧＥＲ　ＷＡＲＮＩＮＧＳ</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 134, 59)\">· · ─────── ·𖥸· ─────── · ·</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 232, 216)\">Be</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 232, 216)\"> a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 231, 216)\">w</span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 231, 216)\">ar</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 231, 216)\">e o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 230, 216)\">f t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 230, 216)\">he</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 230, 216)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 216)\">fo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">llo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 229, 216)\">w</span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 228, 216)\">i</span><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 228, 216)\">ng </span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 228, 216)\">tri</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 216)\">gge</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 227, 216)\">rs</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 227, 216)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 226, 216)\">th</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 226, 216)\">at </span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 226, 216)\">y</span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 225, 216)\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 225, 216)\">u m</span><span style=\"color